38:50.857 --> 38:52.740
I'm going to lift my hand in a minute, pastor.

38:54.142 --> 38:57.989
And then I'm going to take the next step and the next step, the pastor, including the prayer.

38:58.449 --> 39:00.352
I want Jesus to be the center of my life.

39:00.633 --> 39:05.621
I want to turn my love forward to him, or I want to reset my life at the very beginning of a brand new year.

39:06.442 --> 39:07.404
Heads about eyes closed.

39:07.424 --> 39:09.387
If that's you, just lift your hand right now.

39:09.427 --> 39:11.691
Would you just, I care about you.

39:12.913 --> 39:13.714
I love you.

39:14.274 --> 39:15.716
God wants to do something great in your life.

39:16.057 --> 39:17.058
Lift your hand up high.

39:17.078 --> 39:17.940
That's action.

39:18.400 --> 39:19.302
You made the decision.

39:19.342 --> 39:22.006
It has to be followed by action being a doer.

39:22.467 --> 39:23.769
Just lift your hand up high.

39:23.789 --> 39:25.211
Wave it at me in every section.

39:25.792 --> 39:26.853
Keep it up for a second.

39:28.196 --> 39:29.437
Then you could put it back down.

39:30.259 --> 39:31.841
Church, let's all pray this prayer together.

39:32.522 --> 39:32.923
Let's pray.

39:33.143 --> 39:33.944
It's in Romans 10.

39:34.025 --> 39:35.026
We just read it a while ago.

39:35.507 --> 39:38.852
Everyone together, Heavenly Father, I am a sinner.

39:39.633 --> 39:40.695
I repent of my sin.

39:40.715 --> 39:42.738
I believe

39:43.234 --> 39:49.141
Jesus Christ is the Son of God that He died for me and He rose again.

39:49.822 --> 39:52.005
Jesus, come into my life.

39:52.765 --> 39:56.770
I receive you now as my Lord and my Savior.

39:57.551 --> 40:01.296
Jesus is Lord over my life.

40:02.157 --> 40:07.543
Fill me with the Holy Spirit and take my life and make a difference.

40:07.563 --> 40:10.186
In Jesus' name, amen.

40:10.627 --> 40:13.170
Let's look up and celebrate everybody.

40:15.170 --> 40:17.453
